So Windows 10/11 for example is completed in this bit of code:
 https://github.com/netwrix/pingcastle/blob/2d9ab43ba1f4343f5daa983a840a7de08bf28378/Healthcheck/Rules/HeatlcheckRuleStaledObsoleteW10.cs#L21

Then, you can check the Obsolete OS section and check the information under each OS:
